wiki.content:
The second song on the album is "Seven" in this song, Tyler answers his therapist's question "If you had your father's email, what would you tell him?" from the title track. He also talks about how he hates the "Jerking" culture that has sprung up and all the media that wouldn't bother to talk about Odd Future.
